{
  "_comment": "ADLC Salesforce pipeline allowlist — copied into each project's .claude/settings.json by /init. defaultMode is bypassPermissions because /sprint and /proceed run unattended pipelines that fire many routine commands; the allow list below is the safety contract. To require human prompts in your projects, set your user-level ~/.claude/settings.json defaultMode to 'acceptEdits' or 'plan' (project settings override user settings, so set it project-side here too if you want it everywhere). Pre-approves routine git/gh/sf CLI / sf-lint / lint-skills / Apex test / sf agent test / Vlocity preview operations. Production deploys (sf project deploy start, sf agent activate, sf agent publish), Vlocity packDeploy, and destructive data ops (sf data delete/update/upsert/import) currently live in allow for unattended pipeline runs — move them to ask if you want a human gate. git/gh/npm/sh use broad prefix wildcards (anything destructive there is already on the allow list explicitly); sf and vlocity stay granular so the safe/destructive split is auditable.",
  "permissions": {
    "defaultMode": "bypassPermissions",
    "allow": [
      "Bash(git:*)",
      "Bash(gh:*)",
      "Bash(npm:*)",
      "Bash(npx:*)",
      "Bash(sf project deploy validate:*)",
      "Bash(sf project deploy preview:*)",
      "Bash(sf project deploy start --dry-run:*)",
      "Bash(sf project deploy report:*)",
      "Bash(sf project retrieve:*)",
      "Bash(sf project list:*)",
      "Bash(sf data query:*)",
      "Bash(sf data export:*)",
      "Bash(sf data search:*)",
      "Bash(sf data resume:*)",
      "Bash(sf data360:*)",
      "Bash(sf org list:*)",
      "Bash(sf org display:*)",
      "Bash(sf org open:*)",
      "Bash(sf org login web:*)",
      "Bash(sf sobject:*)",
      "Bash(sf sobject describe:*)",
      "Bash(sf sobject list:*)",
      "Bash(sf agent test run:*)",
      "Bash(sf agent test resume:*)",
      "Bash(sf agent generate:*)",
      "Bash(sf agent preview:*)",
      "Bash(sf agent test report:*)",
      "Bash(sf apex run test:*)",
      "Bash(sf apex get test:*)",
      "Bash(sf apex run:*)",
      "Bash(sf apex tail log:*)",
      "Bash(sf apex get log:*)",
      "Bash(sf apex list log:*)",
      "Bash(sf scanner run:*)",
      "Bash(sf force:*)",
      "Bash(vlocity packGetDiffs:*)",
      "Bash(vlocity packExport:*)",
      "Bash(vlocity packDeploy --simulate:*)",
      "Bash(sh:*)",
      "Bash(/bin/sh:*)",
      "Bash(python3:*)",
      "Bash(node:*)",
      "Bash(ls:*)",
      "Bash(mkdir:*)",
      "Bash(find:*)",
      "Bash(readlink:*)",
      "Bash(pwd)",
      "Bash(which:*)",
      "Bash(command:*)",
      "Bash(test:*)",
      "Bash(date:*)",
      "Bash(echo:*)",
      "Bash(cp:*)",
      "Bash(mv:*)",
      "Bash(ln:*)",
